Title: "Cataloguing"
Description:
As ya know, we are here to collect some titan shinies, artifacts, whatever!

And Rannan thinks the more shinies--er, you know what I mean--the better chance we have figurin' out something about the titans.

That'll make Rannan happy, but it'll also ensure I have some extras to take to my store back home.

My wife, Perisimona, is waiting for 'em back in Loamm. I can't go back empty handed!
CompletionText: You get some good shinies yet?
RewardText:
<Tuberros looks at the titan artifacts.>

This one smells very acidic--and it's broken. I can take it to the store... Rannan would like to see that one... Oh yeah, these are great. Thank you for bringing them to me.
